<div id="KIZI">
<h2><i>Lotus japonicus</i> News</h2>

<h3><font color=#steelblue><i>Lotus japonicus</i> genome assembly build 2.5</font></h3>
<b>Kazusa DNA Research Institute is pleased to release <i>Lotus
japonicus</i> genome assembly build 2.5.</b>
<p>
<li><b><a href="http://www.kazusa.or.jp/lotus/summary2.5.html">Summary of build 2.5</a></b></li>
<br>
<li><b><a href="http://www.kazusa.or.jp/lotus/release1/">Database of build 1.0 (previous release)</a></b></li>
</p>
<br>
<font color=#steelblue>publication (May 29, 2008)</font>:<br>
<b><a href="http://dnaresearch.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/content/abstract/dsn008v1">
Genome Structure of the Legume, <i>Lotus japonicus.</i> Sato, S. <i>et al.</i></a></b> <i>DNA Research</i>

<br>
<br>

